high_descs: Turn right and walk to the wall, then turn right and walk to the trash can
Pick up the green apple that is sitting on the white table above the trash can. The table that the microwave is sitting on
Take a right to walk forward, then a left to walk around the table, turn left to face the microwave
Open the microwave and place the apple on the plate inside and then close the door and turn it on. Then open the microwave and pick up the apple and close the door
Turn left and walk to the fridge, halfway across the room turn left and walk to the table that is to the right of the stove then turn right to face the black shelf that is to the left of the sink
Place the apple on the top shelf in the lower right corner
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked apple on a shelf

high_descs: Turn and go to the table in the corner.
Pick up an apple on the small table.
Turn and go to the microwave on the table in the corner.
Cook the apple in the microwave.
Turn and go to the small shelves by the sink.
Put the apple on the small shelves by the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved apple on the small shelves by the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk up the wall, then turn right and walk over to the white table.
Pick up the apple off of the table.
Walk around to the front of the white table so you are facing the microwave.
Open the microwave door then put the apple inside and close the microwave, turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the microwave and take the heated apple out then close the door.
Turn left and walk toward the door, then hang a left and walk across the room, turn right and walk up to the small black shelving unit to the left of the counter.
Put the heated apple on the front right corner of the top of the black shelving unit.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple on top of a black shelving unit.
